   Law Language \& Discourse; Int Journal Legal Discourse; Journal Zhejiang
   Gongshang Univ},
Abstract = {With transnational crime cases increasing yearly and the international
   policing cooperation becoming more regular, it is necessary to improve
   the rapid response ability of police translation. To cope with this
   challenge, the best way is to adopt the big data translation technology.
   The two milestones of this technology are the CAT and MT modes which are
   based on translation corpora. The bigger the corpora, the better their
   effects. But large-scale translation corpora are now in short supply.
   Therefore, we need to carry out research on the construction of
   large-scale translation corpora.},
